<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA45">
<l>viṉaiyār taramuyalum vemmaiyē yañci</l>
<l>tiṉaiyāñ ciṟitaḷavuñ cella niṉaiyātu</l>
<l>vācakattāl lēttiṉēṉ vāṉōr toḻutiṟaiñcu</l>
<l>nāyakattāṉ poṉṉaṭikaḷ nāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fearing the heat those with [bad] karma strive to give</l>
<l>without thinking to swerve even a little that is [the size of] a millet’s [grain]</l>
<l>with [my] speech I have praised the golden feet of the leader</l>
<l>to whom the celestials bow in worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
